data.Name: Travis Tritt
data.Bio: Travis Tritt is an American country music artist. His discography comprises 13 studio albums (counting a Christmas album), six compilation albums, and 43 singles. Of his studio albums, the highest-certified is 1991's It's All About to Change, at 3× Platinum certification by the RIAA and platinum certification by the CRIA. His first, third, and fourth albums— Country Club, T-R-O-U-B-L-E and Ten Feet Tall and Bulletproof, respectively — are all certified double platinum in the US Read more on Last.fm
